data.description: Take a look at this VERY nice home on 2.03 Acres. 3 bedroom 2.5 bath offering 2564 SQ. Ft. Double door entry, spacious foyer. Large living area with floor to ceiling windows, pellet stove. Separate dining room with a Sunroom off the dining room. The kitchen is completely updated, granite tops, top of the line stainless appliances. Double ovens, 3 door refrigerator, pantry and tons of storage space. Garden window in the kitchen.Large laundry room with sink and newer washer and dryer stay. Massive main suite with dressing room and attached bathroom. French doors leading to a deck for your relaxation. Bedroom 2 has access to hall bathroom. This home has central A/C and gas heat. Large oversized garage, with 220, workshop in the back with bathroom. Inground sprinklers front and back, paved circular driveway, Gutters,  Roof approx 5 years old, newer exterior paint.
